  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nIt seems that the last 2048 gossip messages are saved to help prevent duplicate messages.\r\n\r\nI do not believe this is necessary anymore as jvm-libp2p has improved. Removing it would save us a little memory.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/ffdf63eafe666696be70b495983ff1062a3f334c/networking/p2p/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/networking/p2p/libp2p/gossip/GossipHandler.java#L43\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/ffdf63eafe666696be70b495983ff1062a3f334c/networking/p2p/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/networking/p2p/libp2p/gossip/GossipHandler.java#L48\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/blob/ffdf63eafe666696be70b495983ff1062a3f334c/networking/p2p/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/networking/p2p/libp2p/gossip/GossipHandler.java#L81-L89",
